### Get all tariffs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tariffs

### Get tariff by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tariffs/1

### Create new tariff
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tariffs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": null,
  "name": "Test Premium WiFi",
  "features": {
    "downloadMbps": 100,
    "uploadMbps": 50,
    "durationHours": 24,
    "maxDevices": 5
  },
  "pricing": {
    "basePrice": 19.99,
    "currency": "USD",
    "billingType": "ONE_TIME"
  }
}

### Update existing tariff
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tariffs/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Premium WiFi",
  "features": {
    "downloadMbps": 200,
    "uploadMbps": 100,
    "durationHours": 48,
    "maxDevices": 10
  },
  "pricing": {
    "basePrice": 29.99,
    "currency": "EUR",
    "billingType": "ONE_TIME"
  }
}
### Delete tariff
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/tariffs/2